desc: A place to shop for DIY gel kits, no-wipe top coat, rubber base coat, gel colours, and builder gel (BIAB). "You won't get a better gloss than BLOSS!". We are on a mission to make top-quality gel polish affordable & available to everyone (not just qualified nail technicians). Local New Zealand gel business.

layout.text: Long-lasting salon-quality gel polish, tools & kits
